Rtinycc bundles TinyCC as a vendored third-party component.

Bundled component: TinyCC
Upstream repository: https://github.com/TinyCC/tinycc
Vendored source archive: src/tinycc-34eed88.tar.gz
Vendored commit: 34eed88a70fc8238cd5b623cc96b8bf0e40392ed

